# create condition variables for plotting / analyses
cond = [
    (E1_STRnSIB_long['condition'] == 'NoChoice_STR_oblig'),
    (E1_STRnSIB_long['condition'] == 'NoChoice_SIB_oblig'),
    (E1_STRnSIB_long['condition'] == 'Choice_STR_oblig'),
    (E1_STRnSIB_long['condition'] == 'Choice_SIB_oblig')
]

relation = ['Distant', 'Close', 'Distant', 'Close']
choicecontext = ['NoChoice', 'NoChoice', 'Choice', 'Choice']

E1_STRnSIB_long['Relation'] = np.select(cond, relation)
E1_STRnSIB_long['Choice_Context'] = np.select(cond, choicecontext)
